 \begin{align*}& lim_{x\to\infty} \int_x^{2x} sin(1/t) dx\\ = & lim_{x\to\infty} \int_x^{2x} (1/t) + O((1/t)^3) dx\\ = & lim_{x\to\infty} \left[ln(t) + O((1/t)^2)\right]_x^{2x}\\ = & lim_{x\to\infty} \left[ln(2) + O((1/x)^2)\right]\\ = & log(2) \end{align*} 
